---
title: Tahini Pork & Couscous Tabbouleh with Lemon Yoghurt & Flaked Almonds
description: There's couscous and then there's couscous tabbouleh. The key here is to cook it to fluffy perfection, then take it to another level by bringing it together with the fresh and punchy elements of a classic tabbouleh. It serves as the perfect bed for the juicy, tahini-loving pork.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tahini-pork-with-couscous-tabbouleh-7c77b79c.jpg
